{"tid":1638413,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一張圖話你知 裝修之後貼文宣有幾重要！","createTime":"2019-10-08T09:55:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T03:52:21.000Z","uid":63562,"like":88,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"3f53a9069e182a6c82c01ed9d4b677d06d251e17","tid":1638413,"uid":63562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:55:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9v4YR4h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9v4YR4h.png&h=ee5c3614&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n話說頭先小弟路經此處<br />\n見到美心期下嘅東海堂比人裝修完<br />\n有好多中年人啊叔啊嬸係到圍觀影相<br />\n原來係啲封板上面貼左好多文宣去解釋<br />\n有個嬸開波都係到屌：做乜亂咁破壞啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開始仲以為佢係藍嘅<br />\n點知佢睇完文宣講左句:吓乜原來佢係美心架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其他啊叔：喂，咁係美心嘅話，比人搞都唔出奇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n字裡行間，佢地未必完全支持裝修呢個行為<br />\n但佢地起碼可以知道被裝修背後嘅原因<br />\n而唔係覺得後生仔係到鳩破壞<br />\n<br />\n呢件事令我知道<br />\n好多時我地覺得「屌係人都知啦」嘅嘢<br />\n但原來唔係真係全部人都知架<br />\n唔好再停留係自己嘅同温層入面<br />\n的確有唔少師奶啊叔/老一輩/外國人無上開連登<br />\n跟唔上呢場運動嘅步伐<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">緊記</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[black]黑裝修[/black]</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">紅裝飾</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">藍罷買</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">黃幫襯</span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">講好左有個準則就要跟！咪撚學popo啲衰嘢</span></strong><br />\n<strong>不斷去擴大範圍</strong>，<strong>亂咁裝修</strong><br />\n只會令事情<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">失焦</span></span></strong><br />\n希望大家可以不斷提醒自己呢樣嘢！"},{"pid":"5afe4957dcb6b31d247ee4d23366e954bed4d7cb","tid":1638413,"uid":63562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:57:16.000Z","msg":"[black]<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黑裝修</span>[/black]<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e86034d4f83686f5b5d5681f75a3d0161ce5691f","tid":1638413,"uid":66654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:57:34.000Z","msg":"啱  搞任何野都有理由"},{"pid":"6985de1d4c10dec63bba1a79fe699a6da143e6a2","tid":1638413,"uid":121548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:59:07.000Z","msg":"721 811 831 新屋嶺 10.1"},{"pid":"c1eebdeb053faf2ad572a3e38afc7512b7b660be","tid":1638413,"uid":63562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:59:37.000Z","msg":"好多人未行過去睇文宣前，都好似唔知發生乜事咁"},{"pid":"27cb67cab5635d1ea84f08f825edd5bd7732b091","tid":1638413,"uid":63562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:05:33.000Z","msg":"絕對支持神獸同裝修等一切行為，發夢果陣我亦有多次召喚，但都係要人地出手先/持械，一齊都要有個準則，唔好因爲大家都唔割而亂咁黎"},{"pid":"1efd6ab6294cb082eb63d769983d8530eb04554d","tid":1638413,"uid":12006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:06:23.000Z","msg":"推！！！！！！！！！"},{"pid":"4d486404e9a6aba47e36d03df2bb2887d2d63430","tid":1638413,"uid":141976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:13:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bdc3df17f44f8aefb64c0cb11fa64bfda47b9d2","tid":1638413,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:14:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c95606a105a00630e0d805025005d6d4d06e72e5","tid":1638413,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:15:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2310705239056675?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fhkincident%2Fpermalink%2F2310705239056675%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=NaStGCRJdOSKaO4BfYueNiC3g8rst4cc2NZsp