,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a2972266c010393587636dfed1e6bd8c4e90f68","tid":1638413,"uid":193233,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:36:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/shMws1G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FshMws1G.jpg&h=e9f9fbe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢張相都諷刺啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:48:32.000Z","msg":"真講心唔講金"},{"pid":"2db57ecbe7d2af6f47403ff7a66bdd917b4d4028","tid":1638413,"uid":26041,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:49:34.000Z","msg":"文宣新方法！ 以連豬做四格漫畫！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1635818\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1635818</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n見到south park 咁大回響，就發現文宣最緊要易入口，好似 Joan Cornella咁，將每人發生既事記錄落黎，大家睇幾秒就明曬，而且又容易翻譯做唔同語言。而且漫畫容易引人追睇，易入屋又易收藏<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n已經係手足可以幫手畫畫，如果連登仔一齊諗橋，其實一日兩三篇絕對唔難，又可以支援國際戰線，又可以吸引多d人睇！<br />\n<br />\n大家可以幫手諗埋角色設定：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連豬： 深黃勇武派<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連狗： 和理非<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />腦魔： 記者？<br />\n<br />\n其實一開始可以畫d易入口d, 好似老夫子咁深入淺出容易吸引d深黃淺藍 （深黃跟本唔洗睇佢都明<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），又容易translate做其他語言，例如：<br />\n<br />\n1.為所欲為Tee ( 講腦魔教連狗著為所欲為tee，然後比連豬整蠱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 連豬病都冇得帶口罩，變咗豬流感<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.或者用連豬連狗將一d好人好事，黃絲小店分享比大家，例如全民幫黃店清潔同say sorry（或者講下咩店唔幫襯得）<br />\n<br />\n有手足已經幫緊手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NX7PdvS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNX7PdvS.jpg&h=14061a6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家幫手推！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ed9ce97d16a402dc12b4cd86c159a5c07a19a98","tid":1638413,"uid":271305,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:50:31.000Z","msg":"岩！夜間文宣出動"},{"pid":"7595c371a6a6783476c24f8616caed6f3262e4c7","tid":1638413,"uid":200452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f53a9069e182a6c82c01ed9d4b677d06d251e17","tid":1638413,"uid":63562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:55:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9v4YR4h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9v4YR4h.png&h=ee5c3614&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n話說頭先小弟路經此處<br />\n見到美心期下嘅東海堂比人裝修完<br />\n有好多中年人啊叔啊嬸係到圍觀影相<br />\n原來係啲封板上面貼左好多文宣去解釋<br />\n有個嬸開波都係到屌：做乜亂咁破壞啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開始仲以為佢係藍嘅<br />\n點知佢睇完文宣講左句:吓乜原來佢係美心架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其他啊叔：喂，咁係美心嘅話，比人搞都唔出奇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n字裡行間，佢地未必完全支持裝修呢個行為<br />\n但佢地起碼可以知道被裝修背後嘅原因<br />\n而唔係覺得後生仔係到鳩破壞<br />\n<br />\n呢件事令我知道<br />\n好多時我地覺得「屌係人都知啦」嘅嘢<br />\n但原來唔係真係全部人都知架<br />\n唔好再停留係自己嘅同温層入面<br />\n的確有唔少師奶啊叔/老一輩/外國人無上開連登<br />\n跟唔上呢場運動嘅步伐<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">緊記</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[black]黑裝修[/black]</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">紅裝飾</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">藍罷買</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">黃幫襯</span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">講好左有個準則就要跟！咪撚學popo啲衰嘢</span></strong><br />\n<strong>不斷去擴大範圍</strong>，<strong>亂咁裝修</strong><br />\n只會令事情<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">失焦</span></span></strong><br />\n希望大家可以不斷提醒自己呢樣嘢！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:52:02.000Z","msg":"其實仲有好多都係美心 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ESEJ3Fg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FESEJ3Fg.png&h=313c157a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/otZFmrX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FotZFmrX.png&h=1c197c2a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/08vEB0j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F08vEB0j.png&h=47b2fcb5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0e517de7e48217d669dad8cb8da79999c56c45e4","tid":1638413,"uid":277483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:52:09.000Z","msg":"裝修佬裝修完後文字藝術師請馬上去門口接力<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">噴字</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黐文宣</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96e18c2776d7adce81a3d7aa104bcf992e6d69f3","tid":1638413,"uid":193415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:53:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">文宣好重要！！</span><br />\n每人做多少少 可能就唔一樣"},{"pid":"3b9c3a3462bc463a2cf4014e6b9e0504aca73316","tid":1638413,"uid":193415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:54:12.000Z","msg":"文宣好重要！！<br />\n每人做多少少 可能就唔一樣"},{"pid":"bddd8fa6b867f996fdb6d99fdfb6b08c3ed006b6","tid":1638413,"uid":67574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:54:41.000Z","msg":"推，文宣！"},{"pid":"f5dc2fae